metadata.descrtiption: Plaxy NFT is a collection of 1000 hand-designed & animated NFTs with innovative utilities, impactful roadmap steps & strong community. We believe in good-vibes, and we’re all about fun! In Plaxynet you’re a Plaxier, you are the life & soul of the party.Plaxy’s first collection is empowered by ThisOne.
